<title>Element: &lt;replace&gt;</title>

<sect2>
<title>Syntax</title>

<synopsis>
&lt;!ELEMENT replace        (#PCDATA)&gt;
</synopsis>

<para>This element occurs in&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;
<xref linkend="elem_search_replace"/>
</para>

</sect2>

<sect2>
<title>Description</title>

<para>The <command>replace</command> element allows you to specify the
replacement string in a search and replace operation.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2>
<title>Examples</title>

<para>Refer to <xref linkend="elem_search_replace"/> for an example.</para>

</sect2>

